  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Limits: Overview</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loio2b0eda531198434de10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Limits: Overview</h1><div class=\"body\">\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Use\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">You get an overview of limits for the selected limit types by running the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Limits: Overview</span> report. </p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Prerequisites\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Prerequisites</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">You have already created limits. For more information, see also <a class=\"xref\" href=\"ff09da531198434de10000000a174cb4.html\">Editing Limits</a>. </p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Features\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Features</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Selection\n</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrapper tablenoborder\"><table summary=\"\" class=\"table\" frame=\"border\" border=\"1\" rules=\"all\"><colgroup><col width=\"50%\"><col width=\"50%\"></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\"><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Area</span>\n</p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Selection</span>\n</p></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">General Access Options</span>\n</p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><ul class=\"ul\" id=\"loio2b0eda531198434de10000000a174cb4__ul_msx_bj1_4bc\">\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Limit Type</span></p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Limit Currency</span></p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Determination Procedure</span></p></li>\n</ul><p class=\"p\"> </p></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Selection of Limits by Key Date </span></p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Valid To</span>\n</p></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Selection of Limits by Validity Interval\n</span></p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><ul class=\"ul\" id=\"loio2b0eda531198434de10000000a174cb4__ul_u55_rj1_4bc\">\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Valid From</span></p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Valid To</span>\n</p></li>\n</ul></td></tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Output</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">The overview list displays all limits selected according to limit type. </p>\n<p class=\"p\">From this overview, you can branch to the <a class=\"xref\" href=\"370eda531198434de10000000a174cb4.html\">Overview of Limit Utilizations</a> of the individual limits.\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">You can also branch to the business partner data from here.\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">You can display the overview containing data present in the system in different ways. </p>\n</section></div>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
}